Hey Dave,
On my 63 Double cab, I took one of those plastic
holders that have a thingy that hangs over the door at
the base of the window on modern cars and then cut the
little "L" shape from it, then drilled a hole and put
it on where one of my door panel screws are: it works
great!!!


3DPete


